Definition: a swindle in which you cheat at gambling or persuade a person to buy worthless property
Synonyms: verb, social, bunco_game, bunko, bunko_game, con, confidence_trick, confidence_game, con_game, hustle, sting, flimflam, flim-flam, swindle, a, in, which, you, cheat, at, gambling, or, persuade, person, to, buy, worthless, property
Category: noun.act
